video_title: Be an adult and be responsible of your life #motivation #mindset #personalgrowth
transcript:
at some point you just have to grow up
and be a adult if your life is
going to change you have to be the one
to change it you can't blame anyone else
anymore your life is where it is because
you created it to be the way that it is
it's no one else's fault but your own if
you want to keep playing the victim go
for it but it's going to cost you the
life that you want if you do
